Package: v2link-client
Version: 0.1.9.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Udaya Sri <udayasri0@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/UdayaSri0/v2link-client
Depends: libegl1, libgl1, libxkbcommon-x11-0, libdbus-1-3, libxcb-cursor0
Description: Linux desktop client for V2Ray-style links
 Linux desktop client for V2Ray-style links built with Python and PyQt6.
 Runs Xray-core under the hood and provides profile management,
 diagnostics, and desktop proxy integration.
